###Spray and Pray - Replaces Longbow###
### ACTIVATE BEFORE LOADING GAME - NEEDED TO BYPASS SANITY CHECk###
### Reference to Twitch from League of Legends###
### Massive fire rate, Always Corrosive, Infinite ammo.  They don't have ammo in MOBAs. ###

### Weapon Card ###
set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.Name.Title.Title__Unique_Longbow partname Spray and Pray
set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.Name.Title.Title__Unique_Longbow:AttributePresentationDefinition_8 NoConstraintText Shooting's easy, aiming's hard... <br> <font color="#B0FD82">• Infinite ammo, they don't have ammo in MOBAs <br>• Reduced Weapon Damage <br>• INSANE Fire Rate Increase<br>• EPILEPSY WARNING

### Elemental Block - Only Spawns as Corrosive ###
set GD_Weap_SniperRifles.A_Weapons_Unique.Sniper_Hyperion_3_Longbow:WeaponPartListCollectionDefinition_210 ElementalPartData (bEnabled=True,weightedparts=((Part=WeaponPartDefinition'GD_Weap_SniperRifles.elemental.SR_Elemental_Corrosive',Manufacturers=,MinGameStageIndex=0,MaxGameStageIndex=1,DefaultWeightIndex=0)))

### Stats ###
